room_title: Escape room "Kidnapped!" by Race 2 Xcape in Springfield (MO)
room_address: 4560 S. Campbell, Ste L128 Springfield, MO 65810
room_description:
You and your team of detectives have one hour to solve the kidnapping case and escape the room before the FBI is notified and you are fired. Will you become a hero or land in the unemployment line?
There is an exact duplicate of the escape room available and you can compete for the best time with another team. A race between Kidnapped! 1 and Kidnapped! 2 is designed for groups of 12 to 20 people.
